comment: LATR and LHH show Harris (BKN) initially makes contact with the ball, but then makes contact with the left arm of Clarkson (LAL).
Mozgov (LAL) maintains legal guarding position on the drive to the basket and shot attempt by Ferrell (BKN) and any contact is incidental.
Booker (BKN) commits a take foul on Ingram (LAL).
Russell (LAL) legally contests Harris' (BKN) jump shot attempt.
Harris (BKN) commits a take foul on Russell (LAL).
LATR shows Harris (BKN) make contact with Randle's (LAL) arms that causes him to lose control of the ball.
Harris (BKN) commits a take foul on Ingram (LAL).
Randle (LAL) makes marginal contact with Bogdanovic (BKN) that does not affect his drive to the basket and shot attempt.
Bogdanovic (BKN) commits a take foul on Clarkson (LAL).
Mozgov (LAL) cleanly makes contact with the ball on the driving shot attempt by Hamilton (BKN).
Ferrell (BKN) commits a take foul on Russell (LAL).
Russell (LAL) cleanly strips the ball from Bogdanovic (BKN) on the drive to the basket.
